a123d9d94922ae45577f","tid":2187713,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0435aaa522afcb3cf04117e660450b5a1850127f","tid":2187713,"uid":63154,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">王毅說，當今世界百年變局和全球疫情相互叠加，單邊保護主義抬頭，全球化遭遇逆風，國際局勢動盪不定，要維護以國際法為基礎的國際秩序，加強以聯合國為核心的國際體系，攜手推進「後疫情」時代全球治理，共同構建人類命運共同體。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際：企開啲啦屌你老母，呢啲嘢得你感受到咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"共匪係咪將國際米蘭當左係國際咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18263c916b5e0bdf6a174092454d45fd3737c46e","tid":2187713,"uid":260005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"邊11個國家？"},{"pid":"ccf3dbec319759c3cd7cd97cf04a28c6c124771d","tid":2187713,"uid":267932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"首先， 要有人對你嘅人員或者貨物感興趣先。<br />\n然後，繼世衛之後，弱國開始吹風成日提聯合國.... 唔通....."},{"pid":"242cdb1a873eb7c0a05ec26e35ebdb4a7b1d32e6","tid":2187713,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"無中國既一律係單邊主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f150a889968bd2ea432d7e55f4f17f2a3c34c31","tid":2187713,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68c806bae37d6d065c5a765f073a29468eed81e0","tid":2187713,"uid":224547,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"c5e29231b800f8268059dc099c84b82b27ff31d9","tid":2187713,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T21:12:08.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅在北京出席二十國集團外長視像會議時強調，面對新挑戰，多邊主義是唯一選擇。<br />\n<br />\n王毅說，當今世界百年變局和全球疫情相互叠加，單邊保護主義抬頭，全球化遭遇逆風，國際局勢動盪不定，要維護以國際法為基礎的國際秩序，加強以聯合國為核心的國際體系，攜手推進「後疫情」時代全球治理，共同構建人類命運共同體。<br />\n<br />\n王毅說，中方願意與各方攜手發起「人員與貨物跨境流動便利化倡議」，推動雙邊和區域人員和貨物便利化安排形成網絡。<br />\n<br />\n王毅又表示，面對百年一遇的嚴重疫情，二十國集團當務之急是加快疫苗研發、生產和分配，建立抗疫「防火牆」。中國正與11個國家合作開展第三期臨床試驗，將在疫苗研製成功後，通過多種途徑與方式與各國共享。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547746-20200904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547746-20200904.htm&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=ce1f97d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547746-20200904.htm&h=718dcaec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547746-20200904.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T21:14:57.000Z","msg":"屌到小王縮哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeef477bd37ba25b90f787471df165f4cc5eb140","tid":2187713,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"道咗歉未?<br />\n捷克做嘢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a48fe6a88c2f8eff2b75449dc7a8ac16282baf","tid":2187713,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"習總話內循環經濟喎，仲講多邊主義，有無聽書㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a8c8ea4c927ae58c585fae1d7b48376b3c9f4a","tid":2187713,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:32:41.000Z","msg":"中國式多邊主義 係你多邊佢繼續單邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2cb2ff7386607c67ac7bffda1dae5afd81721","tid":2187713,"uid":19013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor